Output output/09_multi_select.mp4

Set FontSize 17
Set Width 800
Set Height 260
Set Padding 16

Hide
Type "deno run -A 09_multi_select.ts"
Enter
Wait+Screen@10s /days of the week/
Show
Sleep 800ms
Space
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 300ms
Down
Sleep 300ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Wait+Screen@30s /Picked/
Sleep 500ms
